metadata.name: Gensler Comes for Crypto
metadata.description:
Hey there crypto enthusiasts...

Looks like the SEC has finally caught on to the latest trend - crypto! Maybe they were too busy regulating the stock market to notice, but hey, better late than never, right?

Now they're cracking down on those crypto players like they're busting up a wild west saloon. We can only imagine the rage fueled ire of the SEC as they start their enforcement actions under the watchful eye of Gary Gensler. We hope they don't get too carried away with their newfound crypto powers!

But fear not, folks, we've got the perfect solution for you - invest in a time machine and go back to when crypto was just a fun internet meme. Just make sure you don't accidentally invest in Dogecoin instead of Bitcoin!

Thanks for tuning in, and don't forget to HODL (hold on for dear life)!

Yours in laughs and crypto chaos, SpecialAgentK.eth.
